12.short_description: Chilean company with a triple-impact sustainable scientific-technological base that provides solutions to construction and energy markets.

18.description:
Chilean company with a triple-impact sustainable scientific-technological base, which manages revalue recycled plastics and construction waste with the aim of transforming them into products that contribute to reducing the planet's carbon footprint in the construction and energy industries.

We break the paradigms of manufacturing, creating new industrial processes in which we take the entire operation towards sustainability, to be the type of company that the future needs.

For this, it was necessary to create and patent an algorithm that allows different residues to be added to a "sustainable concrete" formula from which different products are born, such as wall and floor coverings, home furnishings, "green gravel" and other generic uses of concrete. But also, we cover solutions for all type of plastics by renovating them and transforming into pyro-oil.

By reducing the carbon footprint while building and generating energy, we add value to the industry, we are a differentiated company that will focus its commercial efforts towards a more exclusive market segment.
